<p>This is the input most brands forget. Your <a href="/blog/increase-organic-traffic/">organic traffic data</a> belongs in the model. Pull weekly organic sessions, organic conversions, and keyword rankings from <a href="/blog/google-search-console-guide/">Google Search Console</a> or <a href="/blog/google-analytics-4-setup/">Google Analytics 4</a>.</p>
