<h3>What Happens When You Add SEO to the Model</h3>
<p>Brands that add organic search to their MMM typically discover 2 things.</p>
<p>First, paid search ROAS drops. The model reveals that some paid search conversions would have happened organically. That branded search campaign capturing existing demand gets less credit once organic traffic enters the picture.</p>
<p>Second, content investment shows higher ROI than expected. The lagged, compounding nature of SEO means its true lifetime value is 3-5x what monthly <a href="/blog/measure-content-marketing-roi/">content marketing ROI</a> calculations suggest.</p>
